  "title": "Lorry Driver",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Driving and Delivery:</strong> Transporting goods, materials, or passengers to designated locations.</li><li><strong>Loading and Unloading:</strong> Assisting with the physical movement of items onto and off the lorry.</li><li><strong>Vehicle Maintenance:</strong> Ensuring the lorry is in good working condition, including basic checks and reporting any issues.</li><li><strong>Safety Compliance:</strong> Adhering to traffic laws, road safety regulations, and company safety procedures.</li><li><strong>Customer Service:</strong> Interacting with customers during deliveries, potentially representing the company.</li></ul>",
